    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.20.12"/>
                 
                <note type="curatorial">Missouri Collection</note>
                <fw type="curatorial">12</fw>
                
                
                <fw type="letterhead">
                    <hi rend="caps">DUELL, SLOAN, &amp; PEARCE, INC.
                        <lb/>
                    270 MADISON AVENUE, NEW YORK, N.Y.
                        <lb/>
                    PUBLISHERS
                        <lb/>
                    
                    C. HALLIWELL DUELL
                        <lb/>
                    SAMUEL SLOAN
                        <lb/>
                    CHARLES A. PEARCE
                        <lb/>
                    
                    MURRAY HILL 5-4610
                        <lb/>
                    CABLE:
                        <lb/>
                    SWORDWORDS</hi>
                </fw>                    
                    
                <opener>
                    <dateline>September 22, 1942</dateline>
                
                    <salute>Dear Mr. Neihardt:</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>At the request of Wallace Stegner, I am sending you today a copy of his <hi rend="caps">MORMON COUNTRY</hi> which we shall be publishing the end of this week.</p> 
                
                <p>Mr. Stegner has told me of how great has been your assistance to him and I should like to express our appreciation also.</p>
                <closer>
                    <salute>Sincerely,</salute>
                    <signed>Samuel Sloan</signed>
                
                    <note>SS/fdk</note>
                
                    <address>
                        <addrLine>John <hi rend="caps">G.</hi> Neihardt, Esq.</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>Branson</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>Missouri</addrLine>
                    </address>
                </closer>
                
            </div1>
        </body>
        
